Joey Lawrence https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Joey_Lawrence 0 Joseph Lawrence Migogna Jr. (born April 20, 1976) is an American actor, musician, and game show host. He is known for his roles as Joey Donavan on Gimme a Break, Joey Russo in Blossom, Joe Roman in Brotherly Love, and Joe Longo in Melissa Joey.
